text: Edward Herrera (born 14 November 1986) is a Maltese football player. He plays for Birkirkara and Malta national team. ==Honours== Hibernians * Maltese Cup: 2011–12 * Euro Cup: 2012–13 Birkirkara * Maltese Premier League: 2012–13 ==Other websites== *Profile at MaltaFootball.com Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Maltese footballers
